#. type: itemize
#: ../../../../misc/efaq.texi:581
msgid "The command @kbd{C-h F} (@code{Info-goto-emacs-command-node}) prompts for the name of a command, and then attempts to find the section in the Emacs manual where that command is described."
msgstr "コマンド@kbd{C-h F} (@code{Info-goto-emacs-command-node})はコマンド名の入力を求めて、そのコマンドの記述があるEmacsマニュアルのセクションの検索を試みます。"

