#, no-wrap
msgid "New in Emacs 23"
msgstr "New in Emacs 23"

#. type: section
#: ../../../../misc/efaq.texi:1290
#, no-wrap
msgid "What is different about Emacs 23?"
msgstr "What is different about Emacs 23?"

