#: ../../../../misc/efaq.texi:3845
msgid "To postpone the execution of Emacs Lisp code until after terminal or window-system setup, treat the code as a @dfn{lambda list} and add it to @code{emacs-startup-hook} (or @code{tty-setup-hook} in Emacs 24.4 and newer).  For example,"
