#. type: Plain text
#: ../../../../misc/efaq.texi:4010
msgid "You can swap two keys (or key sequences) by using the @code{keyboard-translate} function.  For example, to turn @kbd{C-h} into @key{DEL} and @key{DEL} to @kbd{C-h}, use"
msgstr ""

